text: Dragana Đorđević (born 2 June 1914, date of death unknown) was a Yugoslav gymnast. She competed at the 1936 Summer Olympics and the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Yugoslav female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
